@startuml alert_context_to_ivi_warning_beep_signal_flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title Alert Context To IVI Warning Beep Signal Flow\n(alert/emergency/road-zone context -> IVI warning beep seams)

participant "Alert / emergency /\nroad-zone context" as AlertCtx #F4F7FB
participant "IVI\nrender owner" as IVI #E8F7E8
participant "UiRender seams" as UiBus #FFF4CC
participant "Observers / audio users" as Obs #E8F0FE

== Beep Inputs ==

AlertCtx -> IVI : alertLevel / alertType\nemergencyType\nroadZoneColorCode
IVI -> IVI : compatBeepEmergency =\n(alertLevel > 0 and emergencyType > 0)
IVI -> IVI : compatBeepIC =\n(alertType in {5,6} and alertLevel > 0)
IVI -> IVI : compatBeepSpeed =\n(roadZoneColorCode in {1,2} and alertLevel > 0)
IVI -> IVI : warningBeepState =\n(compatBeepEmergency + compatBeepIC + compatBeepSpeed > 0) ? 1 : 0
note right of IVI
Representative gating inputs
- alertLevel / alertType
- emergencyType
- roadZoneColorCode
end note

== UiRender Publish ==

IVI -> UiBus : UiRender::beepEmergency / beepIC / beepSpeed
IVI -> UiBus : UiRender::warningBeepState / activeAlertType
note right of IVI
Representative outputs
- beepEmergency
- beepIC
- beepSpeed
- warningBeepState
end note

== Downstream Visibility ==

UiBus -> Obs : warning-beep readback /\naudio/render consumers

note over AlertCtx, Obs
Representative runtime chain
1. Alert, emergency, and road-zone context reach IVI
2. IVI derives the active beep categories
3. IVI publishes warning-beep seams on UiRender
4. Audio/render consumers observe the effective beep posture
end note

@enduml
